page_title: Quickstart - getting started with Azure OpenAI assistants (preview) in AI Studio
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI assistants with new features like code interpreter in AI Studio (Preview).
chunk_content: Clean up resourcesIf you want to clean up and remove an Azure OpenAI resource, you can delete the resource or resource group. Deleting the resource group also deletes any other resources associated with it.- Azure portal- Azure CLIAlternatively you can delete the assistant, or thread via the Assistant's API.
